    "en": {
      "title": "Body of underworld activist found in room",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former underworld activist S. The body of Dayananda alias Kotadaya was found lying under a bed in a two storey house on Ratna Mawatha in Arawwala today, Maharagama Police said.",
        "Police suspect the 55-year-old may have died a few days ago for some reason.",
        "The victims' permanent residence is in the Mirihana Ambuldeniya area, police said.",
        "Police investigations have revealed that he had rented a room upstairs in the two-storey house and was living alone.",
        "The body was found by the 119 Police Emergency Response Unit after receiving information that there was a strong stench in the house.",
        "Police found his mobile phone and earphones under the bed",
        "Police say there was a strong odor when the body was found"
      ],
